      "content": "but \"one small step\" feels like a joke. there's no point in taking steps when there's nowhere to go. everything i do, every single thing, is just for a life that doesn't even feel like mine anymore. i just want the weight to stop. i just want it to be over so i don't have to feel this emptiness anymore.",
